NOTICE ON CLINICAL DATA

This repository was produced as part of the CariSurg MedTech Pathways 2026
Programme in collaboration with Mercer General Hospital.

All patient data referenced in this repository has been fully anonymised.
No patient-identifiable information is stored or shared. The dataset used
(EmergencyTriageDataset_Reduced_Dirty.csv) was provided solely for
educational purposes within the programme.

Any reuse of this repository should respect applicable data protection
legislation and institutional governance standards.
